<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从猴子城回来后，毛克利幸福地住在狼群里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他越长越高，越长越壮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打猎，游泳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他晒太阳，吃了睡，睡了吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在岩石会议上，狼们经常会让毛克利给他们拔爪子上的尖刺。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每次毛克利拔刺，他都会发现一件怪事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果他盯着狼看，狼就会马上避开视线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好奇怪。”他想，“狼们怕我吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利有时候会在森林里看见谢尔坎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利想和他保持距离。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，很多年轻的狼开始效忠谢尔坎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那老虎把剩下的食物扔给他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还称赞他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们真是优秀、勇敢的猎手啊！”谢尔坎温和地说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道为什么你们让阿克拉领导你们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又老又弱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总有一天，毛克利会领导狼群的。”一只年轻的狼说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个人类孩子非常聪明。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他甚至能从我们爪子里拔出刺。”另一只狼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又是那个人类男孩儿！”谢尔坎咆哮道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不如你们其中任何一只厉害！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一些狼也开始咆哮：“你是对的，谢尔坎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利连狼都不是！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉看着狼群里发生的这一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他对此很不满意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛克利，我告诉你多少次谢尔坎是你的敌人了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天下午，他问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个朋友在温暖的阳光下，躺在树叶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像那棵树上的坚果那么多！”他摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉总是警告他，给他建议。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，你听好了。”巴希拉说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿克拉越来越老了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他就会弱得无法领导狼群。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到时候，年轻的狼们会采取行动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们会试图把你赶出狼群。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们不会把我赶出狼群的！”毛克利还是笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我住在森林里，我遵守森林法则。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我甚至还帮我的兄弟姐妹们拔爪子上的刺。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些事情都是事实。”巴希拉坚定地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，你不是狼。你是人类。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>总有一天，你会和人类住到一起的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不那么认为，巴希拉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利打了一个哈欠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有时候，我去山顶观察人类的村庄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我从来没跟村民们说过话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不跟他们一起打猎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>总之，你一辈子都生活在森林里。你不了解人类。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑豹换了一下爪子的姿势，扭过头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很抱歉我说这些话。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，大多数狼都恨你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们认为你比他们更聪明、更健壮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，当你盯着他们看时，他们会扭过头去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们是你的敌人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”毛克利感到刺痛，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好像一只蜜蜂落在了他的皮肤上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以为他们是我的朋友！巴希拉，我该怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一定要保护你自己。”巴希拉说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿克拉领导不了多久狼群了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一旦他在打猎中失败，年轻的狼们就会背叛他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们会到岩石会议上去......</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我知道该怎么办了！”巴希拉笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要下山到山谷里的人类村庄去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>带回几朵人类在那里种的红花。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“红花？”毛克利重复道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>森林里的所有野兽都害怕人类的火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“黄昏时分，红花在他们的小屋外生长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我可以弄到一些。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好！”巴希拉点头说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点弄来一些放在身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等时机到了，你就可以用强大武器做好准备了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>